Worked for a client who is the leading Independent Power Producers in India. They have an installed renewable energy capacity nearing 1.2 GW and are targeting a portfolio of over 3.5 GW project capacity by 2022. They required a solution for remote monitoring and visibility of asset maintenance and servicing.


# Solution Overview
-> Collecting and monitoring performance data from solar panels.
-> Real-time notifications & alerts in case of anomalies.
-> Live dashboard for tracking of all activities.
-> Digital Logbook to log and track data points.
-> Connected Workers- Web & Mobile App for tamper-proof servicing log.
-> Connected Machines- Connectivity to a large number of solar power plants, live monitoring of inverter performance & power generated. Real-time monitoring of equipment anomalies and deviations.
